{
  "id": "RAW_97f84a12",
  "title": "Bengio 15 年前论文再夺 AAAI 奖！AI 正告别单纯炫技，走向真实世界",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MjM5MDE0Mjc4MA==&mid=2651273118&idx=3&sn=b79a8933387304493a328d2f286e38f8",
  "date": "2026-01-26 07:29:00",
  "author": "InfoQ 中文",
  "siteName": "InfoQ 中文",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin:0px 0px 8px;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <p style=\"font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: rgb(145, 145, 145);text-align: left;line-height: 1em;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;margin-top: 13px;padding-left: 14px;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp; 作者 | 木子 </span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">新加坡的会场里，全球人工智能顶会&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">AAAI</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，正式揭晓年度奖项，也迎来了它的第 40 个年头。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">今年共颁发了 5 个杰出论文奖，以及 2 个经典论文奖。在获奖名单中，竟然还有“机器学习三巨头”之一的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Yoshua Bengio</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过这一次，他并不是因为最新成果获奖，而是凭借&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 2011 年写的一篇论文获得了经典论文奖。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;而且不久前，他刚达成 AI 领域首个“百万被引作者”的成就。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">为什么 10 多年前的这篇论文，会在今年被重新拉出来，还获得了经典论文奖？</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不妨来看看它讲了些什么。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名为 Learning Structured Embeddings of Knowledge Bases</span><span leaf=\"\">（《面向知识库的结构化表示学习》）。提出了一种方法，把知识库的结构化数据嵌入到连续空间中，从而让结构化知识更容易用于机器学习任务。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，这篇文章解决的是如何把离散世界（知识、事实、关系）嵌入到连续空间；以及如何让神经网络不靠纯统计，而是“接住现实结构”。而今天热门的世界模型、RAG、Agent 的外部记忆等等这些东西，从本质上讲，全都在复用这条路线。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">再说回今年获奖的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">5 篇杰出论文</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，这些论文有讲机器人和 VLA 的，有在讲如何在连续时间系统中让 AI 模型“白盒化”的，还有讲 LLM 和 CLIP、讲高频信号和局部判别结构的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789385\" data-ratio=\"0.6049953746530989\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2162\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=767d880e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVMXIWYMSQqrHf4ibyq7WQVGSuqMjDFqh5QSUX3a3dAjLhC1luib5mkyYg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">串起来看，这些论文的研究方向，其实可以概括出一个&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">共同指向：AI 的竞争，已从拼实验环境的中的炫酷 Demo，转向真正的应用层。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">Scaling Law 那套虽然不完全失效，但多少有点过时了，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">谁能在真实世界中被理解、被修订、被信任越来越关键。</span></strong></p>\n   <div data-role=\"outer\" label=\"edit by 135editor\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <div data-role=\"paragraph\">\n     <div style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:16px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:0px;\">\n      <div style=\"margin-left:0px;font-size:20px;margin-top:0px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:0px;text-align:center;\">\n       <p><span data-cacheurl=\"\" data-remoteid=\"\" style=\"height: 57px;line-height: 62px;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);border-bottom: 2px solid rgb(0, 179, 139);background: url(&quot;https://image.jido.dev/20260127073706_e2e9d3f.jpeg&quot;) 50% 50% / 55px no-repeat;margin-top: 38px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;display: inline-block;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;AAAI 2026: AI 走向现实，</span></span></strong></span></p>\n       <p><strong style=\"background-color: initial;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);caret-color: red;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">评奖标准重塑</span></span></strong></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">下面来看看这几篇杰出论文，都有哪些有意思的信息。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-left:0px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin-top: 30px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);font-weight: 500;\"><span leaf=\"\">具身智能领域：</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">ReconVLA: Reconstructive Vision-Language-Action Model as Effective Robot Perceiver</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（ReconVLA：作为高效机器人感知器的重建式视觉 - 语言 - 动作模型）</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789382\" data-ratio=\"0.07364341085271318\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2064\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b5a78969&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVYQSak3RianyCQDGUbVSDjHTbu6aUjR3RdbBVdTicwv9ziaBmKpTsD9Qicw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">要说清本文的创新点，需要再这里先简单回顾一下什么是 VLA——VLA（Vision-Language-Action）具身智能领域的一个关键模型，可以把视觉感知、语言理解和动作生成统一到同一个模型中，直接根据“看到什么 + 听到什么”，来输出可执行机器人动作。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">不过当前 VLA 的缺陷也是很明显的：比如模型在执行动作时，视觉注意力高度分散；即便模型能“理解指令”，但在复杂场景、多干扰物、长任务中，往往看不准真正要操作的物体。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">结果就是：抓错对象、操作不精确（现实世界对精确度要求很高）、长链任务中途失败等等。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">总之，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">以往 VLA 只监督“动作输出”，几乎不约束“视觉感知过程本身”。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">ReconVLA 的关键思想是</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：不“告诉模型看哪里”，而是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">“逼模型把关键区域重建出来”。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">其核心机制，简单来说，就是模拟人类视觉的“凝视（gaze）”机制，不要求模型输出框，也不输入裁剪图，而是让模型在内部生成一种“重建信号”，去还原“当前要操作的局部区域”。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文还系统性地对比了三类视觉定位（grounding）范式：</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 14px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 0px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">一类是以外部检测器和裁剪图像为代表的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Explicit Grounding</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">一类是先输出目标框、再生成动作的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">CoT Grounding</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"text-align: left;font-size: 16px;\">\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">以及作者提出的&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Implicit Grounding（隐式 Grounding）</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，也就是 ReconVLA 的方式。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789384\" data-ratio=\"0.35782747603833864\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1252\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e988e8ea&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVtcOciciajJNJBE8WqXDoOIGwBafv8TEegXYUNDClmabX585jkg9p4ia0A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">图注：不同范式 Grounding 之间的概念性对比。</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">前两类方法本质上都是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在显式告诉模型“答案在哪里”</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，并未真正改变 VLA 内部的视觉表示和注意力机制。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 ReconVLA 通过重建过程，将关键区域作为一种隐式的视觉监督信号，引导模型生成所谓的“重建 token（reconstructive tokens）”，从而在不引入额外输入或输出的前提下，重塑视觉感知能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">换句话说，它不再让模型“蒙着眼睛试动作”，而是强制模型在每一步决策前，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">先把目标对象看准，再去动手</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-left:0px;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"font-family: Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin-top: 30px;margin-right: 0px;margin-left: 8px;color: rgb(0, 179, 138);font-weight: 500;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于从“结果可解释”，走向“结构可操作”： </span></p>\n   </div>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Causal Structure Learning for Dynamical Systems with Theoretical Score Analysis</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（基于理论评分分析的动态系统因果结构学习方法）</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789381\" data-ratio=\"0.09928057553956834\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1390\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=854de676&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVEhEBVoByKyaWGibuTO9xgVl8dYCtsyj3Qha8xroibh9NbNGhZ2CbnNibQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这篇论文提出了一种方法：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">CADYT</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。能够在连续时间、甚至不规则采样的数据中，同时刻画系统的动力学演化，并恢复其中的因果结构。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789383\" data-ratio=\"0.4274611398963731\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1544\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85e86c18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVVUogCOVMwR5icLUtib2tkLgiaiax6e1xM0RO7ibcVJoia5hAHzzCBuJM5vNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">更重要的是，作者证明了用于判断因果关系的评分函数，在理论上等价于一种合理的模型选择准则，而不是经验性的启发式指标。换句话说，就是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这个评分</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;不是凭经验设计的，而是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">从理论上保证：它会偏向那些“解释得刚刚好、不多也不少”的因果结构。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">在现实世界的系统中，无论是工业控制、物理系统，还是医疗过程，系统本质上都是连续时间演化的，而且由稳定的因果机制驱动。</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">但以往的方法往往只能解决其中一半问题。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">一类是时间序列因果发现方法，它们通常基于离散时间建模（如 DBN、Granger），并假设规则采样，因此在面对真实的连续动力学和不规则采样时，难以准确刻画系统本身的演化机制。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">另一类是连续时间动力学建模方法（如 Neural ODE、GP-ODE），虽然能自然处理不规则采样，却主要关注预测精度，本质上并不区分因果依赖与偶然相关。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这就留下了一个长期存在的空白：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">几乎没有方法，既工作在连续时间框架下，又能够同时恢复系统的动力学机制和因果结构。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">而 CADYT 正是针对这一空白提出的。它将连续时间的高斯过程动力学建模，与基于最小描述长度（MDL）和算法马尔可夫条件（AMC）的因果评分结合起来，在不规则采样条件下，通过比较不同因果结构对数据的“压缩能力”，来识别真正的因果关系，并给出了明确的理论保证。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">说得更直白一点，这项工作&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">把连续时间动力学建模</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，从“拟合得像不像真实轨迹”，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">推进到了“学到的机制在因果上是不是对的”。</span></strong></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">Model Change for Description Logic Concepts</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">（描述逻辑概念的模型变更）</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789387\" data-ratio=\"0.14213197969543148\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"788\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e41a0ab7&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVUy4ga7Gic2pTzualCBV9xgmG6FvTnr0nnsdqicQBLITwichIDs372jN9A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"padding:23px 8px 0px;margin:0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">此论文还未公开上传，暂无链接。</span></span></p>\n    <div style=\"margin:0;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n     <p style=\"font-family: Avenir,-apple-system-font,微软雅黑,sans-serif;box-sizing: border-box;font-size: 16px;text-align: left;margin: 30px 0 0 8px;color: #00b38a;font-weight: 500;\"><span leaf=\"\">关于表示学习，重新审视结构本身</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM2CLIP: Powerful Language Model Unlocks Richer Cross-Modality Representation</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\">（LLM2CLIP：强大语言模型解锁更丰富跨模态表征）</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789388\" data-ratio=\"0.09416195856873823\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"2124\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=bedee749&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVaS3PMyibT9ZgVR1o413Q5TmicsRnrORK1OU0am67VUKPE03zlWB8DFiaQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">CLIP（Contrastive Language–Image Pre-training）是一个经典的多模态模型，通过对比学习，将图像和文本映射到同一语义空间，从而实现“以文找图、以图找文”等跨模态理解能力。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">CLIP 在跨模态检索和基础语义对齐上表现出色，但它也有一个公认的短板：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">文本编码器容量较小、上下文长度有限，对长、复杂、信息密集的文本理解能力不足</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。这在长文本检索、多语言理解等场景中尤为明显。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM 在语言理解、上下文建模和世界知识方面，倒是明显更强。但问题在于，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM 不能直接接入 CLIP</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">——一方面，原生 LLM 的句向量并不具备对比学习所需的“高区分度”，很难有效拉开不同 caption 之间的距离；另一方面，如果端到端联合训练 LLM 和 CLIP，计算成本也高得不可接受。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这篇论文提出了一种系统化的新方法，名曰：</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">LLM2CLIP</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，顾名思义，</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">把 LLM“接入”或“输送”到 CLIP 里，用 LLM 来替代或者增强 CLIP 的文本能力。</span></strong></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789390\" data-ratio=\"0.8271604938271605\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"972\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78172bfe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVyXQpksOYDdSQ0w72bV4O5wcMibOLCmZ0pib2ibYuTQCbibABUuJ6ePwHAw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">但这并不是简单地把 LLM 直接接进去。作者给出的解决路径，是&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">分两步走，各解决一个关键障碍</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第一步，是先让 LLM 成为一个“合格的文本 embedding 模型”。</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;为此，论文提出了&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">Caption-Contrastive Fine-tuning</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">使用同一张图像对应的不同 caption 作为正样本，通过对比学习，让语义相近的描述在向量空间中更接近、不相关的描述更远；同时配合平均池化、双向注意力和 LoRA 等结构调整，提升句向量的稳定性和可区分性。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">这一步的目标并不是做多模态，而是把 LLM 训练成一个真正“好用”的文本表示器。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">第二步，则是直接用经过处理的 LLM，替换掉 CLIP 原有的文本编码器</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">。在这一阶段，LLM 参数被冻结，仅训练一个非常轻量的 adaptor 来对齐视觉特征，使整体训练流程几乎等同于普通的 CLIP 微调，算力成本基本不变。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">大量消融实验表明：同时保留两个文本编码器、或试图在两者之间做复杂对齐，效果反而更差；“直接替换”是最简单、也是最有效的方案。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">实验结果显示，LLM2CLIP 在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">长文本检索任务上提升最为显著</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">，短文本检索也有稳定增益，同时多语言检索能力明显增强。更重要的是，这些提升是在&nbsp;</span><strong style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">仅使用百万级数据、几乎不增加训练成本</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;的前提下实现的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">总体来看，LLM2CLIP 的价值在于，它没有重造一个更大的多模态模型，而是用一种低成本、可复用的方式，把“语言理解”这块短板，直接补进了 CLIP 的核心结构里。</span></p>\n   <blockquote>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">论文名：</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">High-Pass Matters: Theoretical Insights and Sheaflet-Based Design for Hypergraph Neural Networks</span></p>\n    <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">（高频信息的重要性：面向超图神经网络的理论分析与 Sheaflet 方法设计）</span></p>\n   </blockquote>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503789389\" data-ratio=\"0.0784557907845579\" style=\"width: 100%;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1606\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=08dc5466&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FYriaiaJPb26VMqicTKjGTibMMqOSp5IzGibhVcrhpzWUaopUluUdkTFD4t2oLuPW3gFYfbYFyECckVkGwzKicfpS842Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-left:0px;font-weight:400;font-size:14px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n    <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:center;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\">此论文还未公开上传，暂无链接。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\">总而言之，这些研究都在把关注点从结果层面的性能，推向模型内部的感知、结构和机制本身。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">论文地址：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.10333\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.10333</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2411.04997\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2411.04997</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.14361\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2512.14361</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-weight: bold;\">参考链接：</span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://aaai.org/about-aaai/aaai-awards/aaai-conference-paper-awards-and-recognition/\" target=\"_blank\">https://aaai.org/about-aaai/aaai-awards/aaai-conference-paper-awards-and-recognition/</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://aaai.org/about-aaai/aaai-awards/aaai-classic-paper-award/?utm_source\" target=\"_blank\">https://aaai.org/about-aaai/aaai-awards/aaai-classic-paper-award/?utm_source</a></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin-left:0px;padding:23px 8px 0px;white-space:pre-line;font-weight:400;font-size:16px;font-family:Avenir, -apple-system-font, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;line-height:27px;margin-top:0px;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;margin-right:0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);\"><a href=\"https://aaai.org/conference/aaai/aaai-26/award-talks/\" target=\"_blank\">https://aaai.org/conference/aaai/aaai-26/award-talks/</a></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文通过解读 AAAI 2026 获奖论文，指出 AI 研究正从追求实验环境下的 Demo 效果转向解决真实世界的理解、因果与信任问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文通过解读 AAAI 2026 获奖论文，指出 AI 研究正从追求实验环境下的 Demo 效果转向解决真实世界的理解、因果与信任问题。",
  "summary": "文章聚焦于 AAAI 2026 年度奖项，重点分析了 Yoshua Bengio 的经典论文奖以及数篇杰出论文。核心观点认为，AI 领域正经历从单纯追求 Scaling Law 和炫技 Demo 向真实应用层落地的转型。获奖论文涵盖了具身智能（ReconVLA 通过隐式重建提升感知精度）、动态系统因果学习（CADYT 填补连续时间动力学与因果发现的空白）、以及多模态表征（LLM2CLIP 低成本增强 CLIP 文本能力）等前沿方向。这些研究共同指向一个趋势：未来的 AI 竞争关键在于模型在复杂现实环境中的可解释性、结构化知识处理能力以及对因果机制的掌握。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "AI 竞争重心正从实验环境 Demo 转向真实应用层。",
      "explanation": "单纯的 Scaling Law 边际效应递减，行业开始关注模型在真实世界中是否可理解、可修订、可信任，强调解决实际复杂场景下的精确度问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "具身智能 VLA 模型需从单纯监督动作转向约束视觉感知过程。",
      "explanation": "ReconVLA 提出的隐式 Grounding 机制通过强制模型重建关键区域，模拟人类凝视，解决了机器人在复杂长链任务中看不准、抓错对象的问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "连续时间系统的因果结构学习是实现 AI 白盒化的关键。",
      "explanation": "CADYT 方法将动力学建模与因果评分结合，使 AI 能在不规则采样数据中识别真正的因果关系，而非仅仅进行数据拟合。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用 LLM 增强 CLIP 是提升多模态理解能力的低成本路径。",
      "explanation": "LLM2CLIP 通过两步走策略，将 LLM 转化为高性能文本表示器并替换 CLIP 原有编码器，显著提升了长文本和多语言检索效果。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "AI 的竞争，已从拼实验环境的中的炫酷 Demo，转向真正的应用层。",
    "谁能在真实世界中被理解、被修订、被信任越来越关键。",
    "不再让模型“蒙着眼睛试动作”，而是强制模型在每一步决策前，先把目标对象看准，再去动手。",
    "这项工作把连续时间动力学建模，从“拟合得像不像真实轨迹”，推进到了“学到的机制在因果上是不是对的”。",
    "LLM2CLIP 的价值在于，它没有重造一个更大的多模态模型，而是用一种低成本、可复用的方式，把“语言理解”这块短板，直接补进了 CLIP 的核心结构里。"
  ],
